  • Classes in com.att.research.xacml.api.pip used by com.att.research.xacml.api.pip 
    Class and Description
    PIPEngine
    PIPEngine is the interface that objects implement that do look-up of Attributes.
    PIPException
    PIPException extends Exception to represent errors that can occur as a result of querying a PIPEngine for Attributes.
    PIPFinder
    PIPFinder is the interface objects implement that can query multiple sources of Attributes based on a PIPRequest.
    PIPFinderFactory
    PIPFinderFactory is the factory class for getting the configured PIPFinder.
    PIPRequest
    PIPRequest is the interface that objects implement to represent a request to a PIPEngine to retrieve attributes with values that meet a given request.
    PIPResponse
    PIPResponse is the interface that objects implement that represent a response from a PIPEngine.
